_sText:
This is my first map to be shared amongst the general CSS gungame community - 
its not the first of my creations but its my first decent and popular map, worthy of sharing.

we run this map on our gungame server, so if you want to try it out there, 
its in the rotation on: 85.236.100.89:27115

The map itself isnt massive and offers up some intense gun fighting and close range, 
its been quite popular on our servers and so i have chosen to release it in case anyone 
else wants to try it :D

there are some minor flaws in the map though - on some walls the shadow can be seen through it, 
if someone wants to modify the map file (keeping the original file name and modelling within) 
please contact me for the original hammer file @ info@orion-webhost.com

Also its been a while since i created the map and cant remember how many slots there are, my GG server
is 28 man so i know its got that many slots :)


Cheers,
AG.Kal
